t: "Ask ňĻthem, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúHave you considered your associate-gods which you invoke besides Allah? Show me what they have created on earth! Or do they have a share in ňĻthe creation ofňļ the heavens? Or have We given the polytheists a Book, which serves as a clear proof for them? In fact, the wrongdoers promise each other nothing but delusion.‚ÄĚ"